<a name="q1"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>How do I submit a resume?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">You may submit your resume along with your profile by establishing an account and using our Candidate Profiler. The Candidate Profiler can be accessed in this section.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q2"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Can I submit my resume to a local Banking Center?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">No. Resumes are only accepted online.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q3"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Can I submit my information without applying for a position?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Yes. You are not required to apply for a specific position. If you don't find an opportunity that you are interested in, you can submit your profile only by logging in and using our Candidate Profiler. If you choose to apply later, your profile information will be saved.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q4"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What are the basic requirements for becoming an associate for Bank of America other than the job related qualifications listed in the posting?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">You must be willing to:</p>
	<ul id="answ4" style="list-style-image : url(../images/bull3.gif);">
		<li>Submit authorized documents within three days from the start of employment as proof of authorization to be employed in the United States.</li>
		<li>Be fingerprinted if requested by Bank of America or as required by applicable law, for purposes of conducting a criminal background check.</li>
		<li>Undergo a screening for illegal drugs prior to or during my employment with the Company if requested or as legally required.</li>
	</ul>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q5"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Will I be considered for other positions when applying for a specific position?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Yes, both your candidate profile and resume will be stored in our database - and will be available to our recruiters nationwide.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q6"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>How often can I update my profile?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Once you have established a profile on our site, you are able to access your profile at any time. If there is a change in your skills or employment history - you can log in to make updates.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q7"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What happens to my resume after it's been submitted?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Once submitted, your resume enters our candidate tracking system which utilizes state-of-the-art technology. This tool provides us with a centralized talent pool and serves as the first stop for our recruiters, who are trying to identify candidates for specific job openings.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q8"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>After I submit my profile and/or application will I receive a response?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Yes. You will receive an email confirming that your profile and/or application has been received.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q9"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Will I hear back from a Recruiter?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">You are most likely to receive a response and/or advance through the process if the position to which you apply closely matches your skills and background. If you are not contacted by a Recruiter, please continue to visit our site to search for new available opportunities.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q10"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>How could I be notified if there are new positions that fit my skill set?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Within your Candidate Profile you can designate your "Job Preferences" included are your preferred job Location(s) as well as other specifications. After choosing your preferences, you must activate the checkbox indicating that you would like to receive notifications. If a newly posted position matches your designated preferences, you will be notified via email.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q11"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Where can I find information on insurance plans available to associates?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Visit the section entitled Benefits and click through to Insurance Plans.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q12"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Is diversity important to Bank of America?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">At Bank of America our goal is to draw on the strength of every individual by promoting a diverse workplace. Learn more by clicking on the section diversity.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q13"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What are the lines of businesses that an employee could work within?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Bank of America is comprised of seven lines of business which are all essential to the bank's overall financial success. You can learn more each of the lines of business by accessing Corporate Information.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q14"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Are there flexible work arrangements available?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Our associates enjoy options such as flex-time, compressed workweeks, telecommuting, select time and phase-in. To read more on these options click through to Benefits and Work/Life Balance.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q15"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What is the process as a new employee to coming onboard?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">New associates are given full support when coming on board with Bank of America. To learn more about the process visit Our Staffing Process section.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q16"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Where could I read more on the financial success of Bank of America?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">To understand more of where Bank of America has been and where the company 	is continuing to grow click through to corporate information and the link for Annual Report.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q17"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Is there a sense of team while working at Bank of America?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Team Bank of America is a worldwide organization where associates and retirees can work together in community volunteering programs. Learn more by clicking through to Corporate Information and Community.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q18"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Does Bank of America have a policy on hiring relatives of current associates?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">We do not have a written policy concerning hiring family members, relatives and close friends of current employees or the Corporate Board of Directors. We review each situation on an individual basis.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q19"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Do I have to attend a school full-time to attend a school event?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">No, however most career centers require students, who participate in on-campus events, to be currently enrolled or alumni who have graduated within the last 12 months.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q20"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Are these all the events Bank of America attends?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Yes, however there may be last minute additions or changes that occur which are not updated. Please check with your Career Center for the most up to date list.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q21"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>How can I invite Bank of America to attend my school?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">We use a number of factors to determine our campus recruiting calendar. These factors are evaluated on an annual basis to determine the final list of schools that best meet our needs for each recruiting season.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q22"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What if my school isn't listed, can I attend any event?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Unfortunately, no. Most career centers require students who participate in on-campus activities and events to be enrolled as a student. We recommend that you review our college recruiting page to apply for employment opportunities.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q23"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>Do I get one-on-one time with a Bank of America recruiter at events?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">Yes, but in some cases that time depends on the type of event. Some events have limited time for one-on-one interaction because of the size and scope.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

<img src="../images/clear.gif" width="100%" height="1" alt="" border="0" style="background: #becede;">
<a name="q24"></a><H2 class="p" style="margin: 9px 0px 6px 0px;"><b>What if I missed an event at my school?</b></H2>
<p style="margin: 0px;">If you happen to miss an event, we recommend you check with your career center to obtain contact information of recruiters who visited your college.</p>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 6px 0px; text-align: right;"><a href="#qtop" class="p" onfocus="this.className='p-over';" onblur="this.className='p';" style="text-decoration: none;"><img src="../images/back_to_top.gif" width="7" height="4" alt="" border="0" align="top" hspace="4">Back to Top</a></p>

